Package: GXEadjustedNMR
Title: GxE-Adjusted Nonlinear Mendelian Randomization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yifan", "Kong", email = "kongyifan@hust.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a GxE-adjusted nonlinear Mendelian randomization workflow. 
    The package wraps fastGxE and mmSuSiE outputs, constructs GxE-adjusted exposures, 
    computes main-effect PRS, performs ranked-stratification nonlinear MR, estimates 
    LACE, and provides plotting utilities.
